item.title: ActII
item.description: Mobile analysis # Firstly we need to download both versions If you don’t have jadx install it and open it with “jadx-gui” Hit open file and then select SantaSwipe.apk In “Source Code com northpole.santaswipe MainActivity database” we see SELECT Item FROM NormalList WHERE Item NOT LIKE '%Ellie%' So im guessing Ellie is the answer Yep that gets us the silver Drone path # We find a login page and an “available files” page which we download a .

item.title: ActI
item.description: cURLing # To get silver the commands are fairly simple curl curlingfun:8080 curl -k https://curlingfun:9090 curl -k https://curlingfun:9090 -d 'skip=alabaster' curl -k https://curlingfun:9090 -H 'Cookie: end=3' curl -k https://curlingfun:9090 -I curl -k https://curlingfun:9090 -H 'Stone: Granite' curl -k https://curlingfun:9090/../../etc/hacks --path-as-is And i got the silver medal But how do we get the gold curl -k -X POST https://curlingfun:9090 -d 'skip=bow' -H 'Cookie: end=10' -H 'Hack: 12ft' curl -k https://curlingfun:9090/../../etc/button --path-as-is curl -k -L https://curlingfun:9090/GoodSportsmanship Frosty Keypad # this is the terminal

item.title: Prologue
item.description: Prologue # In this write up we will be going through and solving Holiday hack 2024 The first challenge is Elf connect # For Elf Connect “randomElf” suspiciously has a high score of 50,000 points which ismt possible as 1600 is the highest Firstly we will be opening most of these challenges in their own tab so that theyre esaier to work with The way to do this is right click and insepect and then find the challenge and open in a new tab
